OL,7,FA Wakefield van driver has been jailed
OL,8,Ffor killing a pensioner when he was at
OL,9,Fthe wheel.
OL,11,FQabir Hussain, 54, of Lovaine Grove in
OL,12,FWakefield, hit David Brooke as he
OL,13,Fcrossed Barnsley Road on 17 January
OL,14,F2022.
OL,16,FAnalysis of Hussain's mobile phone
OL,17,Fshowed it had been unlocked during his
OL,18,Fjourney and he had used it to access
OL,19,Fhis emails and a web browser.
