OL,7,FJust seconds later the phone was used
OL,8,Fto dial 999 following the fatal
OL,9,Fcollision.
OL,11,FHe was found guilty of causing death
OL,12,Fby dangerous driving following a trial
OL,13,Fat Leeds Crown Court last month and on
OL,14,FTuesday 21 October he was sentenced to
OL,15,Ffive years behind bars. He was also
OL,16,Fdisqualified from driving.
