OL,7,FPaying tribute to David, his
OL,8,Fgranddaughter said: "My granddad
OL,9,Fshould still be here. The day you took
OL,10,Fhim away from me and my family will
OL,11,Flive with me forever.
OL,13,F"You took the kindest, funniest, most
OL,14,Floving man, everyone loved him. He
OL,15,Fenjoyed life and his family. Most of
OL,16,Fall his wife, my grandma; you have
OL,17,Fbroken her.
