OL,5,Cgranddad
OL,7,F"I miss his voice and hearing his
OL,8,Fstories, his smile and the way he said
OL,9,Fhe loved me. All I have now is
OL,10,Fmemories of my grandad. We love and
OL,11,Fmiss him every day."
OL,13,FDS Nina Roper from the Major Collision
OL,14,FEnquiry Team said: "This case
OL,15,Fhighlights the heartbreaking
OL,16,Fconsequences that can come from a
OL,17,Flapse of concentration at the wheel.
