OL,7,F"Using a phone while driving is one of
OL,8,Fthe 'Fatal Five' offences, which are
OL,9,Fthe top contributory factors in
OL,10,Fserious and fatal collisions.
OL,12,F"No email, message, phone call or
OL,13,Fnotification is more important than
OL,14,Fsomebody else's life. If you really
OL,15,Fneed to use your phone, pull over in a
OL,16,Fsafe place.
